  "folder": "wfo1b78X1ygRgdoN",
  "name": "Outfit - Nomad Leathers (G&C Ver)",
  "type": "clothing",
  "img": "systems/cyberpunk-red-core/icons/compendium/default/Default_Clothing.svg",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The rugged and time-tested clothing of the great outdoors. Made to last, either by nomads themselves or from a bygone era when that was the norm. Leather jackets, jeans (real ones, not the skimpy junk worn by city rats), cowboy hats, goggles, and above all, an assurance that be it heat, cold or dust, it won't bother you.</p><p>After being bought:</p><ul><li><p>The user declares what type of control skill it's been customized to be comfortable in - <strong>land, sea, air, or riding</strong>.</p><ul><li><p>Select the relevant effect from the effects tab, and delete the remainder.</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Once a week while being worn, the user gains <strong>+2 to Wilderness Survival, Endurance, and their declared control skill</strong> for 12 hours.</p></li><li><p>Can be sourced by any fixer or found at any Night Market.</p></li><li><p>Characters can only benefit from one outfit's provided bonuses at a time.</p></li></ul>"
    },
